Minute of a conference held at the United States consulate at Ningpo,
                                Chusan, this morning, the 13th day of January, 1862. President,
                                Captain I. Corbett, her Majesty’s royal naval steamer Scout;
                                President, Willie P. Mangum, United States consul at Ningpo;
                                President, Frederick Harvey, her Majesty’s consul at Ningpo.
